			My hope is that this blog serves as a source of inspiration and motivation for other moms who also 
			love to run and code. I'll be sharing tips on how to balance motherhood, running, and coding, as well as my personal experiences and reflections on this journey.
			Whether you're a seasoned runner or just starting out, a professional coder or a beginner, I invite you to join me on this adventure of pushing boundaries, 
			overcoming obstacles, and pursuing passions. Let's lace up our running shoes, power up our laptops, and take on the world, one code and mile at a time.
